## LUWRAIN~Books

[The~cloud service LUWRAIN Books](local:https://books.luwrain.org/) creates audiobooks of~uploaded texts utilizing commercial text-to-speech engines
and with~the support of~the DAISY format.
This~innovation was based on~considerable research into the~areas of~natural language processing,
parsing of~source materials, and layout generation.
LUWRAIN Books also takes care of~delivering its audiobooks to~readers in~a~way which helps them to~manage bookmarks.

